        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 1. Diversity of Pyrgomorphidae. A. Psedna nana (Rehn, 1953) (Australia: Western Australia); B. Atractomorpha sp. (Papua New Guinea: New Britain); C. Monistria concinna (Walker, 1871) (Australia, NSW); D. Sphenarium histrio Gerstaecker, 1884 (Mexico, Oaxaca); E. Zonocerus elegans (Thunberg, 1815) (South Africa, KZN); F. Dictyophorus spumans (Thunberg, 1787) (South Africa: KZN). Photo credit: (A, B, C, E, F) Hojun Song; (D) Ricardo Mariño-Pérez." ;
